<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="quarrel-n">quarrel <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kwɒrəl/    美 /'kwɔːrəl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>争吵；吵架：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A <strong>quarrel</strong> broke out <strong>between</strong> them.
他们之间发生了口角。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>have a quarrel with sb about / over sb / sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She had a quarrel with her husband about housework.
她因家务事与丈夫吵了一架。</p></div></div>